relation.text: s Commission of the Peace , AND Oyer and Terminer , and Gaol-Delivery of Newgate , Held for the CITY of London , and COUNTY of Middlesex , at Justice-Hall in the OLD-BAYLY . On Wednesday

September , 1707 . In the Sixth Year of Her MAJESTIES Reign , BEFORE the Right Honourable Sir Robert Bedingfeld , Kt . Lord Mayor of the City of London , Sir Thomas Trevor , Kt . Ld . Chief Justice of the Court of Common Pleas , and Sir Selathiel Lovel , Kt . Recorder of the City of London , with divers of her Majesties Justices of Peace , for the City of London , and County of Middlesex . The Jurors were as followeth . London Jury .
